<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=African-American_history&action=edit&section=28.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=African-American_history&action=edit&section=29.php.html" title="Edit section: Surveys">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Surveys">Surveys</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>Earle, Jonathan, and Malcolm Swanston. <i>The Routledge Atlas of African American History</i> (2000) <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/0415921422/">excerpt and text search</a></li>
